<figureCitation box="[430,498,547,573]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1768,1792]" captionTargetBox="[183,1419,631,1742]" captionTargetId="figure-176@2.[166,1420,631,1742]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Megastylus (Dicolus) mentouense Sheng &amp; Li, sp. nov. Holotype. Male. 1 Habitus, lateral view 2 Head, anterior view 3 Head, dorsal view 4 Head and pronotum, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5848333" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5848333/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="457">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
). Body length approximately 5.0 mm. Fore wing length 
<quantity box="[1158,1250,547,574]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" pageId="2" pageNumber="457" unit="mm" value="4.5">4.5 mm</quantity>
. Antenna length 5.0– 
<quantity box="[201,289,583,610]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.3" pageId="2" pageNumber="457" unit="mm" value="5.3">5.3 mm</quantity>
